title=Internet Chat: Creating a custom protocol using sockets
topics=<p>Key Topics Covered in this Tutorial:</p>\n<p>-&#9;A walk through the Internet chat client and server applications</p>\n<p>-&#9;How to view the scripts and examine the object properties</p>\n<p></p>